14:50.123 --> 14:51.658
- I'll get some warrants.

14:51.691 --> 14:53.026
- Thanks.

14:55.562 --> 14:59.499
- You want Trey's computer?
- All electronic devices.

14:59.532 --> 15:02.035
- And what about Luke?
