15:05.038 --> 15:07.307
- We're also gonna need
to search Trey's room.

15:07.340 --> 15:09.409
- You're acting
like my son's the killer.

15:09.442 --> 15:10.978
This is outrageous!

15:11.011 --> 15:12.679
- Just let them go.

15:12.712 --> 15:14.481
They're not gonna find anything.

15:16.149 --> 15:17.985
- Fifteen's a crazy age.

15:18.018 --> 15:19.686
Testosterone, impulses.

15:19.719 --> 15:23.957
- Yeah, but you don't just wake
up one morning out of the blue

15:23.991 --> 15:26.693
