15:29.662 --> 15:31.698
there's something else
going on here.

15:31.731 --> 15:34.734
I don't know. Everything here,
though, looks good.

15:34.767 --> 15:38.638
There's no weed. No booze.

15:38.671 --> 15:43.143
The only thing wrong is maybe
a couple of dirty socks.

15:43.176 --> 15:45.712
- Check this out.

15:47.614 --> 15:50.550
- That's the mother?

15:50.583 --> 15:52.319
Dr. Keller?

15:59.326 --> 15:59.792
- Imagine our surprise.

16:01.228 --> 16:03.363
- Imagine my surprise.

16:03.396 --> 16:05.465
I had a sense Trey was
stalking me, but now I know.

16:05.498 --> 16:08.701
- You had a sense
Trey was stalking you?

16:08.735 --> 16:12.139
Well, that's very different
from having a bad feeling.

16:12.172 --> 16:15.142
- I wasn't sure, but I am now.

16:15.175 --> 16:17.144
- That's you in the photo,
correct?

16:17.177 --> 16:20.247
- Yes! Eyes closed. Asleep.

16:20.280 --> 16:23.516
Unaware this adult teenager was
taking pictures.

16:23.550 --> 16:25.018
- You mind if we take a look
around?

16:25.052 --> 16:26.319
- Of course not.

16:28.221 --> 16:30.257
- So, just to be clear,

16:30.290 --> 16:33.160
you're saying that Trey walked
up these stairs,

16:33.193 --> 16:36.063
he hopped onto your bed
while you were sleeping,

16:36.096 --> 16:38.198
and he took these photos.

16:38.231 --> 16:40.167
- Well, that's the only thing
that makes sense.

16:40.200 --> 16:44.437
- No. There are other
plausible explanations.

16:44.471 --> 16:46.373
- Do you always sleep naked?

16:46.406 --> 16:47.207
- Sometimes.

16:47.240 --> 16:50.277
Sometimes I sleep
in a nightgown.

16:50.310 --> 16:52.479
Sometimes I sleep
in a Rolling Stones t-shirt.

16:54.281 --> 16:56.549
Are you suggesting I had sex
with that boy?

16:56.583 --> 16:57.684
- Oh, I'm not suggesting
anything.

16:57.717 --> 17:01.454
I'm simply asking why you
and Trey were in bed together,

17:01.488 --> 17:03.456
naked.

17:03.490 --> 17:05.225
- Because he was
obsessed with me

17:05.258 --> 17:06.426
and snuck into my bed.

17:06.459 --> 17:08.228
- And you didn't wake up?

17:08.261 --> 17:10.097
You must be a sound sleeper.

17:10.130 --> 17:12.199
- I am.
Last few months, anyway.

17:12.232 --> 17:13.766
I've been on sleep medication.

17:13.800 --> 17:15.735
- You said you thought
Trey was stalking you.

17:15.768 --> 17:16.969
If that's true,
why did you give him

17:17.003 --> 17:20.140
so much access to your house,
invite him in at 9:00 p.m.?

17:20.173 --> 17:23.276
- Like I said,
I was trying to help him.

17:23.310 --> 17:24.511
- Because of his troubled
home life?

17:24.544 --> 17:27.147
Well, we talked to his parents.
There's no evidence of that.

17:30.183 --> 17:32.752
- Some of my patients are
victims of rape,

17:32.785 --> 17:36.256
and the first thing I tell them
is, "Don't blame yourself."

17:36.289 --> 17:38.358
Well, that's a lot easier said
than done.

17:38.391 --> 17:40.293
- You didn't answer
her question.

17:40.327 --> 17:42.295
- I'm sorry.
What question was that?

17:43.496 --> 17:47.134
- Okay. Dr. Keller,
the night of the shooting,

17:47.167 --> 17:49.602
you were upstairs here
in your bedroom,

17:49.636 --> 17:51.104
in your nightgown.

17:51.138 --> 17:53.106
Trey was downstairs
in the family room,

17:53.140 --> 17:54.274
and nobody else was
in the house?

17:54.307 --> 17:55.775
- That's correct.

17:55.808 --> 17:58.178
- And he didn't try and sneak
up here into your room?

17:59.412 --> 18:01.381
- I'm sorry, lieutenant.
I think it's best

18:01.414 --> 18:03.383
if you and your colleague here
leave.

18:03.416 --> 18:05.385
I'm sensing some
underlying hostility,

18:05.418 --> 18:07.520
and it's making me
very uncomfortable.

18:07.554 --> 18:11.258
- Yeah? And the naked selfies
of you and Trey

18:11.291 --> 18:13.360
are making me
very uncomfortable.

18:16.163 --> 18:19.132
[tense music]

18:19.166 --> 18:23.503
*

18:23.536 --> 18:25.138
- Trey was cool.

18:25.172 --> 18:26.506
He was only here
since September,

18:26.539 --> 18:28.341
but we were friends.

18:28.375 --> 18:30.277
- Were you friends
with Luke Keller, too?

18:30.310 --> 18:33.613
- Yeah. Luke and I have known
each other since kindergarten.

18:33.646 --> 18:37.150
He's a good guy.
A little--

18:37.184 --> 18:38.651
- You can say it.
He's a bit of a nerd.

18:38.685 --> 18:40.620
- Yeah. But he's okay.

18:40.653 --> 18:42.622
- But Luke and Trey were close?

18:42.655 --> 18:44.291
- Yeah. Tight.

18:44.324 --> 18:46.159
Trey kind of looked out
for him.

18:46.193 --> 18:47.394
- And Luke liked Trey?

18:47.427 --> 18:49.596
- He idolized Trey.
- Hm.

18:49.629 --> 18:52.332
- Thought he was a god.

18:52.365 --> 18:54.567
I don't know--it's sort of
crazy, if you think about it,

18:54.601 --> 18:58.638
that Luke ended up killing
his god.

18:58.671 --> 19:01.208
- Thank you, Ethan.
- Yeah.

19:03.276 --> 19:07.614
- I never heard rumors
about Trey and Luke's mother.

19:07.647 --> 19:10.383
Is that really
what you think happened?

19:10.417 --> 19:11.918
- We're not thinking
anything yet.

19:11.951 --> 19:15.622
- Right.
Well, the answer is no.

19:15.655 --> 19:17.457
I never heard anyone suggest

19:17.490 --> 19:19.926
that Trey and Dr. Keller were--

19:19.959 --> 19:22.862
- Okay. Anything else about Trey
you can tell us?

19:22.895 --> 19:25.598
- No. He's a good kid.

19:25.632 --> 19:27.234
For the most part.

19:27.267 --> 19:30.703
- For the most part?
What do you mean by that?

19:32.339 --> 19:34.407
- My son has already told
the police everything he knows.

19:34.441 --> 19:36.609
- Okay, well, we just need
to follow up on a few things

19:36.643 --> 19:38.678
about his relationship
with Trey Franklin.

19:38.711 --> 19:41.914
- Now, Ethan, you told me
that Trey was cool.

19:41.948 --> 19:43.450
Here, have a seat.

19:43.483 --> 19:46.253
- That's right.
- So, there's been no issues

19:46.286 --> 19:48.621
or problems
between the two of you?

19:48.655 --> 19:50.357
- None.
- None?

19:50.390 --> 19:52.459
Okay, well, here's the thing,
Ethan.

19:52.492 --> 19:55.262
We just found out
that you and Trey got suspended

19:55.295 --> 19:57.497
for getting into a fight
a week ago.

19:57.530 --> 19:59.966
- Wait. What's going on here?

19:59.999 --> 20:03.370
- Lying to the police
in a homicide investigation

20:03.403 --> 20:05.372
is a very serious matter.

20:05.405 --> 20:06.306
- Serious enough to derail

20:06.339 --> 20:07.740
that lacrosse scholarship
I heard about.

20:07.774 --> 20:09.942
- Okay, okay. Just--

20:11.678 --> 20:13.446
Tell them what happened.

20:16.983 --> 20:18.718
- Can you leave?

20:20.453 --> 20:24.391
I don't want to talk about this
with you here.

20:24.424 --> 20:27.660
- No. I'm not going anywhere.

20:27.694 --> 20:31.598
- Okay. But what I did--

20:31.631 --> 20:33.733
the reason we fought--

20:36.769 --> 20:38.305
[sighs]

20:38.338 --> 20:39.472
I can't tell you.

20:39.506 --> 20:41.541
- Ethan.
- You don't understand.

20:41.574 --> 20:44.377
- Just tell the truth. Now.

20:47.347 --> 20:49.516
- Your father's right.

20:49.549 --> 20:52.685
Just tell us why you and Trey
got into a fight.

20:59.592 --> 21:01.994
- We need to talk to you
down at the station.

21:02.028 --> 21:04.497
- I already told you
everything I know.

21:04.531 --> 21:06.366
- Yeah? Well,
we talked to Ethan Miller.

21:06.399 --> 21:08.501
You know him, right?
- Sure. He's a friend of Luke's.

21:08.535 --> 21:11.304
- He said that you sexually
assaulted him

21:11.338 --> 21:12.605
10 times, maybe 11.

21:12.639 --> 21:14.441
- That's preposterous.

21:14.474 --> 21:15.775
- Then you moved onto Trey.

21:15.808 --> 21:18.711
Ethan got upset, punched him.

21:18.745 --> 21:21.581
They both got suspended
from school.

21:21.614 --> 21:25.718
- They're kids. They fantasize
about older women.

21:25.752 --> 21:27.654
It's a natural,
healthy fantasy.

21:27.687 --> 21:31.624
- Nope. There's nothing natural
or healthy about statutory rape.

21:31.658 --> 21:33.660
Let's go.
You're coming with us.

21:33.693 --> 21:36.363
*

21:43.102 --> 21:44.203
- Were you having a sexual
relationship with Trey Franklin

21:46.105 --> 21:49.041
prior to the night
