21:49.075 --> 21:51.010
- Like I've been trying
to tell you,

21:51.043 --> 21:52.845
he was obsessed with me.

21:52.879 --> 21:53.980
- That's a yes?

21:54.013 --> 21:56.783
- It's an absolute,
unequivocal no.

21:56.816 --> 21:58.351
- What about Ethan?
That's an absolute,

21:58.385 --> 22:00.086
unequivocal no, too?

22:00.119 --> 22:02.054
- Correct.

22:03.390 --> 22:05.091
- So, Ethan was lying?

22:05.124 --> 22:06.759
- Of course he's lying!

22:06.793 --> 22:09.362
- Okay. Well, when he told me
what happened,

22:09.396 --> 22:11.130
he started to cry.

22:11.163 --> 22:11.898
And then he turned
to his father,

22:11.931 --> 22:14.501
and he begged him
not to hate him.

22:16.403 --> 22:19.038
We have a believable
15-year-old boy in there

22:19.071 --> 22:22.909
who is claiming that you
sexually assaulted him

22:22.942 --> 22:24.377
and Trey Franklin.

22:24.411 --> 22:26.112
- Making things worse,
Trey is dead.

22:26.145 --> 22:29.115
- Because you told your son
that he was raping you,

22:29.148 --> 22:31.818
when, in fact,
you were raping him.

22:31.851 --> 22:34.120
- You're making this up.
- The sooner you tell us

22:34.153 --> 22:36.523
the truth, the better this is
gonna be for you.

22:38.458 --> 22:42.862
And more importantly, Luke.

22:42.895 --> 22:46.165
- Don't you presume to tell me
what's best for my son.

22:46.198 --> 22:49.469
- I'm not presuming anything.
I'm just stating facts.

22:49.502 --> 22:51.438
- [scoffs]
My understanding of the law is

22:51.471 --> 22:54.574
unless I'm under arrest,
I'm free to go.

22:56.543 --> 22:57.977
I'll be calling my lawyer.

22:58.010 --> 23:00.413
- That's your right.
We'll be in touch.

23:00.447 --> 23:02.415
I'm sure we'll have a lot
to talk about.

23:02.449 --> 23:05.418
[dramatic music]

23:05.452 --> 23:10.623
*

23:10.657 --> 23:12.425
- She's a stone-cold liar.

23:12.459 --> 23:14.427
- A psychiatrist...

23:14.461 --> 23:16.162
who's abusing teenage boys,

23:16.195 --> 23:20.066
emotionally damaging
her own son.

23:20.099 --> 23:24.203
That is deeper than lying, man.
That is pathological.

23:24.236 --> 23:25.572
- And we just let her
walk out of here?

23:25.605 --> 23:28.107
- Look. I want to track
her phone.

23:28.140 --> 23:29.976
I need to vet Ethan's story.

23:30.009 --> 23:33.179
- She's smart. And a liar like
that--she covers her tracks.

23:33.212 --> 23:34.914
- That's why we need
hard evidence

23:34.947 --> 23:36.182
that she cannot lie
her way out of.

23:36.215 --> 23:38.885
But first we need
to make absolutely sure

23:38.918 --> 23:40.119
that Luke had no prior knowledge

23:40.152 --> 23:43.456
of what was going on
with his mother and Trey.

23:45.091 --> 23:48.661
- That's crazy.
No way would my mom and Ethan--

23:48.695 --> 23:50.497
he's a liar--he's lying.

23:50.530 --> 23:52.031
- Listen.
I know this is hard to hear--

23:52.064 --> 23:53.132
- Because it's not true.

23:53.165 --> 23:55.067
My mom told me
you were gonna say this.

23:55.101 --> 23:56.969
- Just listen to what they say,
Luke.

23:57.003 --> 23:59.238
- I'm sorry
to have to tell you this.

23:59.271 --> 24:01.708
But it's not just Ethan.
We also believe

24:01.741 --> 24:02.642
Trey and your mom were having--

24:02.675 --> 24:05.211
- She said you were gonna
say that, too!

24:05.244 --> 24:08.981
There's no way that--that--

24:11.250 --> 24:13.185
It's just not true.

24:15.555 --> 24:18.224
My mom would never do that.

24:18.257 --> 24:19.626
- Okay.

24:23.162 --> 24:26.165
I think Luke is being
completely honest.

24:26.198 --> 24:29.168
- Well, of course he is.
He's a good kid.

24:29.201 --> 24:30.537
His mother,
on the other hand, is--

24:30.570 --> 24:31.971
- Is what?

24:32.004 --> 24:33.940
- Complicated.

24:33.973 --> 24:35.608
- Dr. Keller,
is there anything

24:35.642 --> 24:38.177
in Nicole's past
or your relationship

24:38.210 --> 24:43.015
that might help explain this--
this type of behavior?

24:43.049 --> 24:45.184
- She is a malignant narcissist,

24:45.217 --> 24:47.520
probably borderline.

24:48.254 --> 24:50.222
I'm a psychiatrist as well.

24:51.323 --> 24:54.193
- So, this lying, manipulating,

24:54.226 --> 24:56.162
abusive pattern of behavior's

24:56.195 --> 24:57.296
been going on for a long time?

24:57.329 --> 24:59.932
- Since the day I met her.

24:59.966 --> 25:02.735
Nicole is like the best
and worst woman you've ever met

25:02.769 --> 25:04.003
wrapped in one.

25:04.036 --> 25:05.538
- Yeah, we've been getting that.

25:05.572 --> 25:07.540
- Well, when we first met,
she's--she's charming.

25:07.574 --> 25:09.075
She's brilliant.

25:09.108 --> 25:12.278
But gradually, her sickness
began to reveal itself.

25:12.311 --> 25:14.581
- How do you mean?

25:14.614 --> 25:15.948
- [sighs]

25:15.982 --> 25:18.284
Look, with Nicole--

25:18.317 --> 25:20.219
this woman truly believes
that she's special,

25:20.252 --> 25:23.690
that she deserves this unique
and constant admiration.

25:25.157 --> 25:28.561
She lacks compassion, empathy.

25:28.595 --> 25:32.599
Yet, at the same time,
she is remarkably fragile.

25:33.633 --> 25:35.768
She has no true sense of self,

25:35.802 --> 25:37.570
and I--I just--
I couldn't take it.

25:37.604 --> 25:40.239
- So you left her.
- Yes.

25:40.272 --> 25:41.974
Yes. Look, but I tried
to make it work.

25:42.008 --> 25:43.576
I-I couldn't.

25:43.610 --> 25:47.346
- You just let Luke stay there,
live with her,

25:47.379 --> 25:49.582
knowing Nicole has
all these issues?

25:49.616 --> 25:51.718
- No. I fought like hell
for custody,

25:51.751 --> 25:53.352
but the judge sided with her,
because, I'm telling you,

25:53.385 --> 25:57.556
this woman--she is incredibly
charming and persuasive.

26:04.030 --> 26:06.132
I never thought
she'd destroy her own son.

26:10.236 --> 26:12.138
Just tell me you're not gonna
charge Luke with a crime.

26:12.171 --> 26:14.106
- Your ex-wife is
the criminal here.

26:14.140 --> 26:15.675
We're gonna speak with the ADA.

26:15.708 --> 26:20.079
*

26:20.112 --> 26:22.682
I don't think that Luke
intentionally shot Trey.

26:22.715 --> 26:25.284
He truly believes that his
mother was being assaulted.

26:25.317 --> 26:26.585
- I agree.
Council, look.

26:26.619 --> 26:29.756
Luke had no clue that his mother
was using his friends sexually.

26:29.789 --> 26:31.323
He just happened to walk in.
I mean, if he hadn't

26:31.357 --> 26:33.192
gotten into an argument
with his father that night,

26:33.225 --> 26:35.094
he never would've been there
in the first place.

26:35.127 --> 26:37.163
Nicole is the one who's lying,
not Luke.

26:37.196 --> 26:38.765
- And this proves it.

26:38.798 --> 26:41.768
Lab results are back.
Traces of fresh semen were found

26:41.801 --> 26:43.836
on a towel in Nicole's bedroom
upstairs.

26:43.870 --> 26:44.771
DNA matches Trey's.

26:44.804 --> 26:46.773
- She said Trey was upstairs
that night?

26:46.806 --> 26:49.408
- We asked her point blank,
and she denied it.

26:49.441 --> 26:52.879
- Arrest her.
- Statutory rape?

26:52.912 --> 26:54.847
- Oh, I'm thinking a lot more
than that.

26:58.184 --> 27:00.419
- Let's talk about that.
- Okay, time's up.

27:00.452 --> 27:01.754
- What?
- I'm sorry, sir.

27:01.788 --> 27:03.189
NYPD. We're gonna need the room.

27:03.222 --> 27:04.056
- Are you kidding me?
- Nope.

27:04.090 --> 27:06.625
- Look,
just get out of here, man. Go.

27:08.360 --> 27:10.329
- First, you lie to my son.

27:10.362 --> 27:12.331
Now you harass me
in my place of business?

27:12.364 --> 27:14.200
- Stop talking.
You're under arrest.

27:14.233 --> 27:15.334
- On what charges?

27:15.367 --> 27:17.269
- Third degree rape
of a minor.

27:17.303 --> 27:19.672
- I'm the victim here.
- And murder.

27:19.706 --> 27:22.208
- Murder?
I didn't murder anyone.

27:22.241 --> 27:24.443
- Look, lady. Turn around.
Come on.

27:24.476 --> 27:26.178
- Get her out of here.

27:27.179 --> 27:29.148
[handcuffs clicking]

27:35.121 --> 27:36.055
[overlapping shouts]
- Okay, look, look, look.

27:36.956 --> 27:38.124
Our only goal was
to follow the evidence

27:38.157 --> 27:40.159
and bring the person responsible
for Trey Franklin's death

27:40.192 --> 27:43.863
to justice, and that person is
Nicole Keller.

27:43.896 --> 27:45.197
To cry rape while she herself

27:45.231 --> 27:46.899
was sexually assaulting
a teenage boy

27:46.933 --> 27:49.001
with her son ten feet away,
holding a rifle,

27:49.035 --> 27:51.403
shows such depraved indifference
to Trey Franklin's life

27:51.437 --> 27:54.874
that the DA's office feels
compelled to punish this woman

27:54.907 --> 27:56.075
to the fullest extent
of the law.

27:56.108 --> 27:57.744
Thank you.

27:57.777 --> 28:01.147
- We applaud Mr. Barba's courage
in taking on this case.

28:01.180 --> 28:04.717
Our 15-year-old son, Trey,
was abused by a manipulative

28:04.751 --> 28:07.019
and remorseless 45-year-old
psychiatrist.

28:07.053 --> 28:09.155
Because of her, he's dead.

28:10.923 --> 28:12.424
Let's go.

28:12.458 --> 28:15.427
- Last Tuesday night,
Dr. Nicole Keller

28:15.461 --> 28:17.964
was the victim
of a sexual assault,

28:17.997 --> 28:19.899
and if it weren't for
the actions of her son, Luke,

28:19.932 --> 28:21.801
she might have been killed.

28:21.834 --> 28:24.503
Dr. Keller is a respected
and empathetic psychiatrist

28:24.536 --> 28:26.906
who was simply trying
to help Trey Franklin,

28:26.939 --> 28:29.075
and despite the fact
that he sexually assaulted her,

28:29.108 --> 28:32.211
she is devastated
by his tragic death.

28:32.244 --> 28:35.047
And to suggest that she had
anything to do with this

28:35.081 --> 28:37.917
is absolutely outrageous.

28:37.950 --> 28:40.052
[reporters all speaking at once]

28:42.188 --> 28:44.156
- Lieutenant Benson, this towel,
marked exhibit D,

28:44.190 --> 28:45.992
