44:38.977 --> 44:41.279
- Luke! I love you.
- Nicole, no.

44:41.312 --> 44:43.949
- And I forgive you!

44:43.982 --> 44:46.985
I do! Do you hear me?
Do you hear me?

44:47.018 --> 44:49.988
I'm still your mother!

44:50.021 --> 44:53.825
I'll always be your mother,
no matter what you've done!

44:53.859 --> 44:56.995
I will always be your mother!

44:57.028 --> 44:59.931
- Let's go.
- Congratulations, Lieutenant.

44:59.965 --> 45:01.299
You've convinced my son
I'm the devil.

45:01.332 --> 45:03.368
- No, Nicole.

45:03.401 --> 45:05.370
You did that all by yourself.

45:15.146 --> 45:16.915
- You okay?

45:18.249 --> 45:20.251
Look.

45:20.285 --> 45:23.088
He's a strong kid.
He'll be fine.

45:23.121 --> 45:25.991
- You really believe that?

45:26.024 --> 45:27.192
- [sighs]

45:27.225 --> 45:29.160
Can I buy you a drink?

45:30.829 --> 45:33.899
- No, thanks.
I got to go home to see Noah.

45:33.932 --> 45:35.767
I got to--

45:35.801 --> 45:37.936
I just want to be with my boy.

46:01.126 --> 46:01.259
.

